<P>Permanent Death? Oooooh I like it!

<P>Though I don't see ANYONE over level 30... ever...
<P>Whole zones would be left empty for all intensive purposes (Kedge, Mistmoor, Solusek and Permafrost), leaving the newbie zones teeming with pre-teen psychopaths. Could you imagine East Commons?!? I would definitely play it for quick PvP fix, but I doubt I'd make it a home server.
<P>Would permanent death only happen with PvP? Or both PvP and NPCs?
<P>Either way, I think it would be a great experimental server.
<P>--Eirik the Red
